'''''Better Dead Than Alien''''' is a [[fixed shooter]] published in 1988 for the [[Amiga]], [[Atari ST]], [[Commodore 64]] and [[MS-DOS]] by Electra.<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://amr.abime.net/review_48233|title=Better Dead Than Alien review from Amiga Computing Vol 1 No 4 (Sep 1988) - Amiga Magazine Rack}}</ref>

A fixed shooter allowing some vertical movement, the player takes control of hero Brad Zoom's ship in his quest to save civilization from aliens. The game is full of humor and the intro screen is in magazine style.

